{"id": "13162", "revid": "53418829", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=13162", "title": "Ulthring", "text": " is one of the generals of the former &lt;a href=\"League%20of%20the%20Damned\"&gt;League of the Damned&lt;/a&gt; and a weaponsmith.\nBackground.\nThe archmage Ulthring served as the leader of the &lt;a href=\"Legion%20of%20the%20Damned\"&gt;Legion of the Damned&lt;/a&gt; in their second attack on the &lt;a href=\"Ferol\"&gt;Ferol&lt;/a&gt; dynasty. Aside from his magical powers, Ulthring wore a red battle armour and wielded the &lt;a href=\"Sword%20of%20Lies\"&gt;Sword of Lies&lt;/a&gt;, a mighty blade forged by himself, containing a seed of the &lt;a href=\"Lord%20of%20Chaos\"&gt;Lord of Chaos&lt;/a&gt;' soul.\nDuring the battle, Ulthring used his powers to kill many of the members of &lt;a href=\"the%20League%20of%20Seven\"&gt;the League of Seven&lt;/a&gt;. However, at some point in the battle Ulthring and the Lord of Chaos were separated from their army by the armies of the League of Seven. From here he was shot in the left eye with an arrow by &lt;a href=\"Ralph\"&gt;Ralph&lt;/a&gt;. Ulthring writhed in the ground whilst the leader of the &lt;a href=\"wizard\"&gt;wizard&lt;/a&gt;s, &lt;a href=\"Ruben%20Ferol\"&gt;Ruben Ferol&lt;/a&gt;, defeated the Lord of Chaos. Following the battle, Ralph, in his anger, reached for the Sword of Lies and pierced it through Ulthring's throat."}
{"id": "4521", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=4521", "title": "Ulthring's Cuirass", "text": " is a &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Knight%20Saga%20Armour%23Unique%20Armour%20List\"&gt;special armour&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nDescription.\nUlthring's cuirass is a &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Knight%20Saga%20Armour%23Unique%20Armour%20List\"&gt;special cuirass&lt;/a&gt; and is a component of the &lt;a href=\"Ulthring%27s%20Set\"&gt;Ulthring's Set&lt;/a&gt;, which is constituted of &lt;a href=\"Ulthring%27s%20Helmet\"&gt;helmet&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Ulthring%27s%20Cuirass\"&gt;cuirass&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Ulthring%27s%20Gauntlets\"&gt;gauntlets&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Ulthring%27s%20Leggings\"&gt;leggings&lt;/a&gt;. It requires atleast level 28 in order to be worn. When worn the cuirass will boost Ranged Armour Rating by 5 points and &lt;a href=\"Spirit\"&gt;Spirit&lt;/a&gt; attribute by 12 points and &lt;a href=\"Vitality\"&gt;Vitality&lt;/a&gt; attribute by 5 points. Furthermore it will grant its wearer 1 point in &lt;a href=\"Regenerate\"&gt;Regenerate&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Knight%20Saga%20Skills\"&gt;skill&lt;/a&gt;. The cuirass has 1 charm slot and 2 enchantments slots. \nHow to Obtain.\nDropped by General &lt;a href=\"Stone\"&gt;Stone&lt;/a&gt; at &lt;a href=\"Stone%27s%20Flying%20Fortress\"&gt;Stone's Flying Fortress&lt;/a&gt;, if he was &lt;a href=\"mindread\"&gt;mindread&lt;/a&gt; prior to the fight.\nSet Properties.\nUlthring's Cuirass is a part of the set Ulthring's Set which allows the item to gain additional, potentially increasing, properties the more items of the same set are worn. Ulthring's Cuirass primary increased attribute is Melee Armour Rating, which is firstly gained by equipping 2 items from the set, and then increased by equipping more items from the set. "}
{"id": "4520", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=4520", "title": "Ulthring's Gauntlets", "text": " are a &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Knight%20Saga%20Armour%23Unique%20Armour%20List\"&gt;special gauntlets&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nDescription.\nUlthring's gauntlets is a &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Knight%20Saga%20Armour%23Unique%20Armour%20List\"&gt;special gauntlets&lt;/a&gt; and is a component of the &lt;a href=\"Ulthring%27s%20Set\"&gt;Ulthring's Set&lt;/a&gt;, which is constituted of &lt;a href=\"Ulthring%27s%20Helmet\"&gt;helmet&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Ulthring%27s%20Cuirass\"&gt;cuirass&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Ulthring%27s%20Gauntlets\"&gt;gauntlets&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Ulthring%27s%20Leggings\"&gt;leggings&lt;/a&gt;. It requires atleast level 26 in order to be worn. When worn the gauntlets will boost Magic Armour Rating and Melee Armour Rating by 4 points each. Alongside increased armour rating the gauntlets will add bonus 10 points into &lt;a href=\"Vitality\"&gt;Vitality&lt;/a&gt; attribute and grant 1 point of the &lt;a href=\"Life%20Leech%20%28Dragon%20Knight%20Saga%29\"&gt;Life Leech&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Knight%20Saga%20Skills\"&gt;skill&lt;/a&gt;. The gauntlets have 1 charm slot and 2 enchantment slots. \nHow to Obtain.\nDropped by &lt;a href=\"Xanlosch\"&gt;Xanlosch&lt;/a&gt; at &lt;a href=\"Stone%27s%20Flying%20Fortress\"&gt;Stone's Flying Fortress&lt;/a&gt;, if he was &lt;a href=\"mindread\"&gt;mindread&lt;/a&gt; prior to the fight. \nSet Properties.\nUlthring's Gauntlets is a part of the set Ulthring's Set which allows the item to gain additional, potentially increasing, properties the more items of the same set are worn. Ulthring's Gauntlets primary increased attribute is Magic Armour Rating, which is firstly gained by equipping 2 items from the set, and then increased by equipping more items from the set. "}
{"id": "4519", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=4519", "title": "Ulthring's Helmet", "text": " is a &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Knight%20Saga%20Armour%23Unique%20Armour%20List\"&gt;special helmet&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nDescription.\nUlthring's Helmet is a &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Knight%20Saga%20Armour%23Unique%20Armour%20List\"&gt;special helmet&lt;/a&gt; and is a component of the &lt;a href=\"Ulthring%27s%20Set\"&gt;Ulthring's Set&lt;/a&gt;, which is constituted of &lt;a href=\"Ulthring%27s%20Helmet\"&gt;helmet&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Ulthring%27s%20Cuirass\"&gt;cuirass&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Ulthring%27s%20Gauntlets\"&gt;gauntlets&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Ulthring%27s%20Leggings\"&gt;leggings&lt;/a&gt;. It requires atleast level 30 in order to be worn. When worn the helmet will boost Magic Armour Rating by 5 points and &lt;a href=\"Spirit\"&gt;Spirit&lt;/a&gt; attribute by 8 points. The helmet has 1 charm slot and 3 enchantments slots. \nHow to Obtain.\nThe helmet is obtained by &lt;a href=\"Mindread\"&gt;mindreading&lt;/a&gt; and defeating &lt;a href=\"Black%20Ring\"&gt;Black Ring&lt;/a&gt; general &lt;a href=\"Kali\"&gt;Kali&lt;/a&gt; at &lt;a href=\"Kali%27s%20Flying%20Fortress\"&gt;Kali's Flying Fortress&lt;/a&gt;\nSet Properties.\nUlthring's Helmet is a part of the set Ulthring's Set which allows the item to gain additional, potentially increasing, properties the more items of the same set are worn. Ulthring's Helmet primary increased attribute is Ranged Armour Rating, which is firstly gained by equipping 2 items from the set, and then increased by equipping more items from the set. "}
{"id": "4522", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=4522", "title": "Ulthring's Leggings", "text": " are a &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Knight%20Saga%20Armour%23Unique%20Armour%20List\"&gt;special leggings&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nDescription.\nUlthring's leggings is a &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Knight%20Saga%20Armour%23Unique%20Armour%20List\"&gt;special leggings&lt;/a&gt; and is a component of the &lt;a href=\"Ulthring%27s%20Set\"&gt;Ulthring's Set&lt;/a&gt;, which is constituted of &lt;a href=\"Ulthring%27s%20Helmet\"&gt;helmet&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Ulthring%27s%20Cuirass\"&gt;cuirass&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Ulthring%27s%20Gauntlets\"&gt;gauntlets&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Ulthring%27s%20Leggings\"&gt;leggings&lt;/a&gt;. It requires atleast level 29 in order to be worn. When worn the leggings will boost Melee Armour Rating by 6 points. Alongside increased armour rating the leggings will add bonus 6 points into &lt;a href=\"Spirit\"&gt;Spirit&lt;/a&gt; attribute and grant 1 point of the &lt;a href=\"Evade\"&gt;Evade&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Knight%20Saga%20Skills\"&gt;skill&lt;/a&gt;. The leggings have 2 enchantment slots. \nHow to Obtain.\nDropped by General &lt;a href=\"Raze\"&gt;Raze&lt;/a&gt; in the Headquarters of &lt;a href=\"Raze%27s%20Flying%20Fortress\"&gt;Raze's Flying Fortress&lt;/a&gt;, if he was &lt;a href=\"mindread\"&gt;mindread&lt;/a&gt; before the fight.\nSet Properties.\nUlthring's Leggings is a part of the set Ulthring's Set which allows the item to gain additional, potentially increasing, properties the more items of the same set are worn. Ulthring's Leggings primary increased attribute is &lt;a href=\"Vitality\"&gt;Vitality&lt;/a&gt;, which is firstly gained by equipping 2 items from the set, and then increased by equipping more items from the set. "}
