{"id": "17148", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=17148", "title": "Undeployed Dazzler Trap", "text": " is a type of &lt;a href=\"Munitions%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;ammunition&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nCharacteristics.\n is a throwable trap that deals no damage on its own but inflicts &lt;a href=\"Blinded%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Blinded Status&lt;/a&gt; (2 turns) in 4 meter radius, if the Magic Armour of affected characters reaches 0.\nAll characters can deploy this trap. However due to the trap dealing no damage and only inflicting status effect it is not possible to increase its effectiveness through abilities or attributes."}
{"id": "17154", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=17154", "title": "Undeployed Displacer Trap", "text": " is a type of &lt;a href=\"Munitions%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;ammunition&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nCharacteristics.\n is a throwable trap that deals no damage and inflicts no status effect on its own. Instead this trap will randomly teleport any character that activates it into random area.\nAll characters can deploy this trap. However due to the trap dealing no damage and only inflicting status effect it is not possible to increase its effectiveness through abilities or attributes."}
{"id": "17151", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=17151", "title": "Undeployed Firestorm Trap", "text": " is a type of &lt;a href=\"Munitions%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;ammunition&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nCharacteristics.\n is a throwable trap that deals fire damage and inflicts &lt;a href=\"Burning%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Burning Status&lt;/a&gt; (for 1 turn) in 3 meter radius, if the Magic Armour of affected characters reaches 0. Additionally this trap creates a fire surface at the area of impact (3 meters).\nAll characters can deploy this trap. The damage of the trap depends on &lt;a href=\"Pyrokinetic%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;Pyrokinetic&lt;/a&gt; ability."}
{"id": "17157", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=17157", "title": "Undeployed Nailbomb Trap", "text": " is a type of &lt;a href=\"Munitions%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;ammunition&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nCharacteristics.\nAll characters can deploy this trap. The damage of the trap depends on &lt;a href=\"Warfare%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;Warfare&lt;/a&gt; ability."}
{"id": "17160", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=17160", "title": "Undeployed Poison Gas Trap", "text": " is a type of &lt;a href=\"Munitions%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;ammunition&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nCharacteristics.\n is a throwable trap that deals poison damage and inflicts &lt;a href=\"Poisoned%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Poisoned Status&lt;/a&gt; (for 1 turn) in 3 meter radius, if the Magic Armour of affected characters reaches 0. Additionally this trap creates a poison cloud at the area of impact (2 meters).\nAll characters can deploy this trap. The damage of the trap depends on &lt;a href=\"Geomancer%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;Geomancer&lt;/a&gt; ability."}
{"id": "17163", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=17163", "title": "Undeployed Smoke Trap", "text": " is a type of &lt;a href=\"Munitions%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;ammunition&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nCharacteristics.\n is a throwable trap that deals no damage and inflicts no status effect on its own. Instead this trap will create a smoke cloud in 3 meter radius when any character activates it.\nAll characters can deploy this trap. However due to the trap dealing no damage and only inflicting status effect it is not possible to increase its effectiveness through abilities or attributes."}
{"id": "17166", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=17166", "title": "Undeployed Thunderbolt Trap", "text": " is a type of &lt;a href=\"Munitions%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;ammunition&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nCharacteristics.\n is a throwable trap that deals air damage and inflicts &lt;a href=\"Shocked%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Shocked Status&lt;/a&gt; (for 2 turns) in 3 meter radius, if the Magic Armour of affected characters reaches 0.\nNote that if character is affected by &lt;a href=\"Shocked%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Shocked Status&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"Wet%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Wet Status&lt;/a&gt; this trap will cause the character to be affected by &lt;a href=\"Stunned%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Stunned Status&lt;/a&gt;.\nAll characters can deploy this trap. The damage of the trap depends on &lt;a href=\"Aerotheurge%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;Aerotheurge&lt;/a&gt; ability."}
