{"id": "3826", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=3826", "title": "Ursula", "text": "Ursula is a &lt;a href=\"human\"&gt;human&lt;/a&gt; witch found in the &lt;a href=\"Prancing%20Seahorse%23Forbidden%20Archive\"&gt;Forbidden Archive&lt;/a&gt; at &lt;a href=\"Prancing%20Seahorse\"&gt;Prancing Seahorse&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Aleroth\"&gt;Aleroth&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0in 1300 AD.\nBackground.\nUrsula is a witch on a quest\u00a0to obtain a powerful spell that will allow her to rule a land far away. You are faced with the choice of letting her go in exchange for undoing the vegetable enchantment inflicted upon the Prancing Seahorse members, or killing her.\nStrategy Guide.\nNote: If you let her go, you'll obtain &lt;a href=\"Ursula%27s%20Bow\"&gt;Ursula's Bow&lt;/a&gt; as a gesture of good will. She does not drop the &lt;a href=\"Bows\"&gt;bow&lt;/a&gt; if killed.\nIf you choose to fight Ursula , you must enter the portal to the &lt;a href=\"Hellish%20Dimension\"&gt;Hellish Dimension&lt;/a&gt;. You will be greeted by two groups of minions that you should eliminate before fighting Ursula. Walk off the ledge just to the left of the broken bridge near the upper teleporter, and fall to the ledge below. Facing the rock wall, head to the right and drop down again. Pull the lever next to the teleporter and then enter it. Begin attacking Ursula, and as soon as she teleports to the other area, run into the teleporter and resume attack as soon as you are out. Repeat this process until she is dead. After she has been defeated loot the &lt;a href=\"Vegetable%20Spell\"&gt;Vegetable Spell&lt;/a&gt; from the chest near the teleporter furthest from your entry location."}
