{"id": "14148", "revid": "49426621", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=14148", "title": "Vampiric Ghoul", "text": "Vampiric ghouls are creatures in &lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity\"&gt;Divine Divinity&lt;/a&gt;.\nBackground.\nAlthough their true origins cannot be discerned, theories span from being a creation of &lt;a href=\"The%20Seven%20Gods\"&gt;The Seven Gods&lt;/a&gt;, coming out of a falling star, which crash-landed a long time ago to a coupling &lt;a href=\"vampire\"&gt;vampire&lt;/a&gt;s and &lt;a href=\"ghoul\"&gt;ghoul&lt;/a&gt;s.\nSome drunk &lt;a href=\"dwarf\"&gt;dwarf&lt;/a&gt;, after ten pints of &lt;a href=\"ale\"&gt;ale&lt;/a&gt; even claimed that he knowns someone who read a book called \"Origins of vampiric ghoul\". where it was suggested that they were created by the dark archmage &lt;a href=\"Ragun\"&gt;Ragun&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"Rogar\"&gt;Rogar&lt;/a&gt;, or similar as an attempt to make creature which would be as vile and evil as himself.\nLocation.\nStalker's Cave in the &lt;a href=\"The%20Dark%20Forest\"&gt;Dark Forest&lt;/a&gt;."}
{"id": "12370", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=12370", "title": "Vampiric Hunger", "text": "Vampiric hunger is a &lt;a href=\"Hydrosophist%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;Hydrosophist&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Scoundrel%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;Scoundrel&lt;/a&gt; skill in \"\".\nDescription.\nScroll and Skillbook.\n skillbook is a magical item that allows its reader to learn skill, if they have at least 1 point into both &lt;a href=\"Hydrosophist%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;Hydrosophist&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Scoundrel%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;Scoundrel&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Attributes%20and%20Abilities%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;abilities&lt;/a&gt;, and use it indefinitely. In order to be able to cast the skill, character needs 1 free memory slot. Note that the book will disappear once read. The book weights 0.5 and its base value is 190 gold. A skillbook can be crafted if a any non-source &lt;a href=\"Hydrosophist%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;Hydrosophist&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Scoundrel%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;Scoundrel&lt;/a&gt; skillbooks are combined. Since is a mixed skill, traders do not have the skillbook for sale.\n is one of the few magic-based skills in the game that does not have a scroll.\nLocations.\nTraders.\nThis skill cannot be bought or stolen from any NPCs in the game."}
{"id": "12371", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=12371", "title": "Vampiric Hunger Aura", "text": "Vampiric Hunger Aura is a &lt;a href=\"Hydrosophist%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;Hydrosophist&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Scoundrel%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;Scoundrel&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Sourcery%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;source&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Skills\"&gt;skill&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nDescription.\nSkill.\n is a supportive mixed skill that allows caster to release an aura that grants vampiric powers to their allies in 13 meter range up to 2 turns. This aura grants afflicted allies 50 % Life Steal and as such they are able to heal themselves in proportion to damage done to Vitality (armour not included) of their targets. \n healing is also one of the few ways to properly heal allied &lt;a href=\"Undead\"&gt;Undead&lt;/a&gt; without damaging them.\nSince relies on &lt;a href=\"Hydrosophy\"&gt;Hydrosophy&lt;/a&gt; magic it cannot be cast if caster is affected by &lt;a href=\"Silenced%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Silenced&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Enraged%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Enraged&lt;/a&gt; status effects.\nScroll and Skillbook.\n skillbook is a magical item that allows its reader to learn skill, if they have at least 2 points into both &lt;a href=\"Hydrosophist%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;Hydrosophist&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Scoundrel%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;Scoundrel&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Attributes%20and%20Abilities%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;abilities&lt;/a&gt;, and use it indefinitely. In order to be able to cast the skill, character needs 2 free memory slots. Note that the book will disappear once read. The book weights 0.5 and its base value is 500 gold. A skillbook can be crafted by combining any &lt;a href=\"Hydrosophist%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;Hydrosophist&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Scoundrel%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;Scoundrel&lt;/a&gt; skillbooks out of which atleast one must be a source skillbook. Since is a mixed source skill, traders do not have the skillbook for sale.\n is one of the few magic-based skills in the game that does not have a scroll.\nSkill Modifiers.\n is a supportive skill whose 50 % Life Steal bonus is set and as such this bonus itself cannot be increased. However the amount of health restored will be greater if the damage output of said character is increased as the Life Steal depends on damage done to target characters Vitality.\nNote that 50 % Life Steal is equal to 5 points in &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Necromancer\"&gt;Necromancer&lt;/a&gt; combat ability. However the Life Steal provided by the skill DOES STACK with the Life Steal granted by the Necromancer ability. can also be affected by other skills.\nLocations.\nTraders.\nThis skill cannot be bought or stolen from NPCs in the game."}
