{"id": "3647", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=3647", "title": "Ranger Strength", "text": "Ranger Strength is a &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Knight%20Saga%20Skills%23Ranger\"&gt;Ranger skill&lt;/a&gt; that can be used by &lt;a href=\"the%20Dragon%20Knight\"&gt;the Dragon Knight&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nDescription.\nRanger Strength is a passive Ranger skill that allows the Knight to increase physical damage (not magic damage) done by using bow. Due to its nature, once learnt, it will be always active. "}
{"id": "3589", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=3589", "title": "Ranger Surprise", "text": "Ranger Surprise is a &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Knight%20Saga%20Skills%23Ranger\"&gt;Ranger skill&lt;/a&gt; that can be used by &lt;a href=\"the%20Dragon%20Knight\"&gt;the Dragon Knight&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nDescription.\nRanger Surprise is a active Ranger skill that allows the Knight to shoot a special arrow at their target, weakening them after being hit. This skill requires equipped bow in order to be used, therefore using this skill with melee weapon in hand will cause the Knight to automatically switch to equipped bow."}
