{"id": "22613", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=22613", "title": "Raw Bird Leg", "text": " is a &lt;a href=\"Consumables%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;consumable item&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nCharacteristics.\n is a consumable item which may be used for cooking. When consumed it heals 15 % of maximum Vitality while lowering &lt;a href=\"Constitution\"&gt;Constitution&lt;/a&gt; by 1 point and having 50 % chance to set &lt;a href=\"Diseased%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Diseased&lt;/a&gt; status effect for 2 turns (blocked by physical armour). \nCharacters with &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Talents\"&gt;Five-Star Diner talent&lt;/a&gt; are healed for 30 % of maximum Vitality while their Constitution is lowered by 2 points. The chance to get &lt;a href=\"Diseased%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Diseased&lt;/a&gt; status effect status remains the same as well as its duration. The effect of last 3 turns.\nPoisoned are a consumable item that was poisoned through various means (either &lt;a href=\"Poison%20Bottle%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;poison bottle&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"Zaikk%27s%20Talon\"&gt;Zaikk's Talon&lt;/a&gt;). Poisoning the will reduce its value to 0. Instead of healing it will deal poison damage equal to 15 % of the consumers maximum Vitality, rendering it unsafe for the living but safe for &lt;a href=\"Undead\"&gt;Undead&lt;/a&gt; while lowering &lt;a href=\"Constitution\"&gt;Constitution&lt;/a&gt; by 1 point and having 50 % chance to set &lt;a href=\"Diseased%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Diseased&lt;/a&gt; status effect for 2 turns (blocked by physical armour). \nIf character has &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Talents\"&gt;Five-Star Diner talent&lt;/a&gt; the will deal poison damage equal to 30 % of the consumers maximum Vitality while lowering &lt;a href=\"Constitution\"&gt;Constitution&lt;/a&gt; by 2 points and having 50 % chance to set &lt;a href=\"Diseased%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Diseased&lt;/a&gt; status effect for 2 turns (blocked by physical armour). The effect of last 3 turns. \nNote that poisoned item may be used in crafting, however the end product will be un-poisoned item.\nLocations.\nTraders.\nFollowing NPCs sell a large variety of food and thus have a solid chance (not guaranteed) of having in their stock. Note that as a consumable item may be very randomly sold by other NPCs.\nUsage.\nFollowing table shows all items for which this item is used for. "}
