{"id": "2635", "revid": "49426621", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=2635", "title": "Reaping the Seeds", "text": "Reaping the Seeds is a &lt;a href=\"Ego%20Draconis%20quests\"&gt;quest&lt;/a&gt; obtained in the &lt;a href=\"Primordial%20Cave\"&gt;Primordial Cave&lt;/a&gt; by talking to the dragon head statues that guard a door which must be opened to proceed with the main quest &lt;a href=\"Hall%20of%20Echoes%20Bound\"&gt;Hall of Echoes Bound&lt;/a&gt;. After speaking with the statues, you need to obtain three Magic Seeds to feed them. The &lt;a href=\"Books%20and%20notes%20%28Dragon%20Knight%20Saga%29\"&gt;book&lt;/a&gt; found on the table next to nearby the dead priest, &lt;a href=\"Ancient%20Parchment\"&gt;Ancient Parchment&lt;/a&gt;, provides some background information on the statues. The seeds can be gathered in any order, and each is a sub-quest with its own rewards.\nOnce all the seeds have been gathered, return to the Primordial Cave and talk to each of the statues to complete the quest.\nDetailed Walkthrough.\nThe First Hungry Statue.\nThe first seed is obtained from Jievaras at Camp Courage, east of &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Cliff%20Castle\"&gt;Dragon Cliff Castle&lt;/a&gt;. He asks you to turn into a &lt;a href=\"dragon\"&gt;dragon&lt;/a&gt; and kill three wyverns that have been pestering him. Speak to him again when the task is complete.\nThe Second Hungry Statue.\nThe second seed is acquired from Yggdrasil, on the small island south of the Primordial Cave. He asks you to kill a goblin named Charlie on the northern end of the island. Speak to him again when the task is complete.\nThe Third Hungry Statue.\nThe third seed is received From Irminsul, across the water (east) of the &lt;a href=\"Red%20Hammer%20Tribe\"&gt;Red Hammer Tribe&lt;/a&gt; waypoint shine. He asks you to answer some riddles:\nRewards.\nAfter feeding the statues the seeds you receive the following rewards:"}
