{"id": "15866", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=15866", "title": "Red Snapper (Original Sin 2)", "text": "Red snapper is a &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Consumables\"&gt;consumable item&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nCharacteristics.\n is a consumable food item which heals 10 % of maximum Vitality and grants + 1 bonus point into &lt;a href=\"Intelligence\"&gt;Intelligence&lt;/a&gt; upon consumption. If character has &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Talents\"&gt;Five-Star Diner talent&lt;/a&gt; then it will grants + 2 bonus points into &lt;a href=\"Intelligence\"&gt;Intelligence&lt;/a&gt; and heal 20 % of maximum Vitality. The effect of last 3 turns.\nPoisoned is a consumable item that was poisoned through various means (either &lt;a href=\"Poison%20Bottle%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;poison bottle&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"Zaikk%27s%20Talon\"&gt;Zaikk's Talon&lt;/a&gt;). Poisoning the will reduce its value to 0. Instead of healing it will deal poison damage equal to 10 % of the consumers maximum Vitality, rendering it unsafe for the living but safe for &lt;a href=\"Undead\"&gt;Undead&lt;/a&gt; and grants + 1 bonus point into &lt;a href=\"Intelligence\"&gt;Intelligence&lt;/a&gt;. \nIf character has &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Talents\"&gt;Five-Star Diner talent&lt;/a&gt; the will deal poison damage equal to 20 % of the consumers maximum Vitality and grants + 2 bonus points into &lt;a href=\"Intelligence\"&gt;Intelligence&lt;/a&gt;. The effect of last 3 turns. \nNote that poisoned item may be used in crafting, however the end product will be un-poisoned item.\nLocations.\nTraders.\nFollowing NPCs sell a large variety of food and thus have a solid chance (not guaranteed) of having in their stock. Note that as a consumable item may be very randomly sold by other NPCs.\nUsage.\nFollowing table shows all items for which this item is used for. "}
