{"id": "3947", "revid": "49426621", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=3947", "title": "Reminiscence Of The Past", "text": "Reminiscence Of The Past is a &lt;a href=\"Flames%20of%20Vengeance%20quests\"&gt;side quest&lt;/a&gt; offered by &lt;a href=\"Ricky\"&gt;Ricky&lt;/a&gt;, the bartender and de facto proprietor of the &lt;a href=\"Phoenix%20Inn\"&gt;Phoenix Inn&lt;/a&gt; in the &lt;a href=\"Great%20Market\"&gt;Great Market&lt;/a&gt; district of &lt;a href=\"Aleroth\"&gt;Aleroth&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nDetailed Walkthrough.\nRicky tells you that his mother's amulet (&lt;a href=\"Eleanor%27s%20Necklace\"&gt;Eleanor's Necklace&lt;/a&gt;) has sentimental value and he believes that it protects him from harm. He'd like to get it back, but unfortunately &lt;a href=\"Henry%20and%20Eleanor%27s%20House\"&gt;Henry and Eleanor's House&lt;/a&gt; is in the &lt;a href=\"Crow%27s%20Nest\"&gt;Crow's Nest&lt;/a&gt; district, and due to the infestation of &lt;a href=\"Creatures%23Undead\"&gt;walking dead&lt;/a&gt; he cannot. He'd like you to retrieve it for him.\nIf you have not yet done so, you'll need to complete the quest &lt;a href=\"Bark%20up%20the%20Right%20Tree\"&gt;Bark up the Right Tree&lt;/a&gt; to gain access to the city's Crow's Nest district. Henry and Eleanor's House is in the northwest area of the district, across the road from &lt;a href=\"Servus%20and%20Alina%27s%20House\"&gt;Servus and Alina's House&lt;/a&gt; and the &lt;a href=\"Sewer%20Tunnels\"&gt;Sewer Tunnels&lt;/a&gt; entrance. Be prepared to face level 39 and 40 &lt;a href=\"ghoul\"&gt;ghoul&lt;/a&gt;s, &lt;a href=\"Hell%20Spawn\"&gt;hell spawn&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href=\"skeleton\"&gt;skeleton&lt;/a&gt;s within. Also beware of the pressure plate floor traps throughout the house.\nOnce inside, you'll notice that the house seems to be in a state of disrepair, and has quite a few corpses strewn about. Proceed a short distance north to an intersection, where you'll see two bandits fleeing the undead. Head west at the intersection, then north to a large room with several beds, dealing with the traps and undead along the way. There are three regular &lt;a href=\"chest\"&gt;chest&lt;/a&gt;s here (containing random loot), plus a small chest on a table that contains your objective: &lt;a href=\"Eleanor%27s%20Necklace\"&gt;Eleanor's Necklace&lt;/a&gt;.\nIf you'd like to thoroughly loot the remainder of the house, refer to the &lt;a href=\"Henry%20and%20Eleanor%27s%20House\"&gt;Henry and Eleanor's House&lt;/a&gt; article. Otherwise, return to Ricky at your convenience to complete the quest."}
