{"id": "14922", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=14922", "title": "Remove the Curse", "text": " is a &lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity%20quests\"&gt;side quest&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity\"&gt;Divine Divinity&lt;/a&gt;\".\nWalkthrough.\nFinn, an old farmer tells of an old abbey from where he hears and sees strange noises and light. Head north and west along the Farmlands until reaching the &lt;a href=\"Cursed%20Abbey\"&gt;Cursed Abbey&lt;/a&gt;. In the the grounds and building &lt;a href=\"Lich\"&gt;Lich&lt;/a&gt;es and &lt;a href=\"steel%20skeletons\"&gt;steel skeletons&lt;/a&gt; are waiting. Push through the enemies and head to the kitchen and dining area, to find a hatch down.\nIn the cellar is a long hallway that has been trapped. Head south to the door and then go west to find a locked door; there is a key nearby, but it does not fit the lock. Proceed south to find a lever; pull it and proceed again further south to find another lever which will open the door that was locked before. Return north and through the now open door to find a library and another lich, the &lt;a href=\"Engineer\"&gt;Engineer&lt;/a&gt;, who will engage &lt;a href=\"Lucian\"&gt;Lucian&lt;/a&gt; in conversation. After telling his story, you will have the option to either pay the 1000 gold that he was due in payment from the monks or fight him, which will result in liches and steel skeletons appearing.\nBe sure to grab the magic amulet hidden between two bookshelves next to the &lt;a href=\"Engineer\"&gt;Engineer&lt;/a&gt;."}
