{"id": "10949", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=10949", "title": "Resist All Potion", "text": "The resist all potion is a &lt;a href=\"Consumables%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;consumable item&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nCharacteristics.\nMinor resist all potion will increase resistance to Air, Water, Fire, Earth and Poison by 15 % for 3 turns. If the character has &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Talents\"&gt;Five-Star Diner talent&lt;/a&gt;, all resistances will be increased by 30 %. The potions weight is 0.25 and its value is 200 gold.\nMedium resist all potion will increase resistance to Air, Water, Fire, Earth and Poison by 50 % for 3 turns. If the character has Five-Star Diner talent, all resistances will be increased by 100 %. The potions weight is 0.25 and its value is 375 gold.\nLarge resist all potion will increase resistance to Air, Water, Fire, Earth and Poison by 75 % for 2 turns. If the character has Five-Star Diner talent, all resistances will be increased by 150 %. The potions weight is 0.25 and its value is 650 gold.\nLocations.\nTraders.\nFollowing NPCs sell a large variety of potions and thus have a solid chance (not guaranteed) of having in their stock. Note that as a consumable item may be very randomly sold by other NPCs."}
