{"id": "20589", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=20589", "title": "Rock Rune", "text": " is a type of &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Items\"&gt;magical item&lt;/a&gt; in \"\"\nCharacteristics.\n is a magical item that can be crafted and subsequently inserted into equipment with rune slots in order to grant bonuses to maximum Vitality, Earth Resistance or add additional Earth Damage. These bonuses depend on the rune size and whether it is imbued with rune frames which add additional properties. The bonuses the rune provides are, in most cases, increased with its size. The weight of the rune is 0.1 and remains unchanged through crafting or increasing its size. "}
