{"id": "12389", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=12389", "title": "Medusa Head", "text": "Medusa Head is a &lt;a href=\"Polymorph%20%28Skill%20Class%29\"&gt;novice Polymorph&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Skills\"&gt;skill&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nSkill.\n is a offensive polymorph skill that allows caster to transform their body. skill causes caster to grow snakes upon their head, thus unlocking &lt;a href=\"Petrifying%20Visage\"&gt;Petrifying Visage&lt;/a&gt; skill, which lets them deal earth damage to all hostile characters. Afflicted hostile characters without Magic Armour will be afflicted with &lt;a href=\"Petrified%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Petrified&lt;/a&gt; status for 1 turn. Additionaly the caster gains + 1 point to &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Geomancer\"&gt;Geomancer&lt;/a&gt; ability, increased Earth Resistance by 50 % and immunity to the &lt;a href=\"Petrified%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Petrified&lt;/a&gt; status.\nHostile characters without Magic Armour in 3 meter radius of the caster, will be afflicted with &lt;a href=\"Petrified%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Petrified&lt;/a&gt; status and suffer damage directly to their health, as long as skill is active.\nSince relies on &lt;a href=\"Metamorphosis\"&gt;Metamorphosis&lt;/a&gt; magic it cannot be cast if caster is affected by &lt;a href=\"Silenced%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Silenced&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Enraged%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Enraged&lt;/a&gt; status effects. \nScroll and Skillbook.\n skillbook is a magical item that allows its reader to learn skill, if they have at least 2 points into &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Polymorph\"&gt;Polymorph&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Attributes%20and%20Abilities%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;ability&lt;/a&gt;, and use it indefinitely. In order to be able to cast the skill, character needs 1 free memory slot. Note that the book will disappear once read. The book weights 0.5 and its base value is 190 gold. Since is a novice Polymorph skill, traders will start selling the skillbook once &lt;a href=\"Godwoken\"&gt;Godwoken&lt;/a&gt; reach level 4.\n is a one of the few magic-based skills that does not have a scroll. The skill itself is affected by other skills, attributes and talents that may provide additional bonuses.\nLocations.\nTraders.\nFollowing table shows all NPCs who are guaranteed to sell Polymorph spellbooks, with their location and coordinates in the right column, from them. The location shown in the table (and the coordinates) are only for the initial location the NPC is in. Note that some of these may have other spell/skillbooks and goods to sell. "}
