eir enemies.\nDetailed description.\nList of all skills available.\nMetamorph is a class focused on casting &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Polymorph\"&gt;Polymorph&lt;/a&gt; spells. Following table shows all skills and spells which Metamorph can learn as they level up and invest points in respective combat abilities."}
