{"id": "14193", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=14193", "title": "Meteorstrike", "text": "Meteorstrike is one of the starting &lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity%20skills%23Way%20of%20the%20mage\"&gt;mage skills&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity\"&gt;Divine Divinity&lt;/a&gt;\". \nDescription.\nHurls a small meteor at the position the cursor is clicked in order to cause damage. The skill covers the visible range of the user. The skill book is called Meteor Strike."}
{"id": "2298", "revid": "27868532", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=2298", "title": "Method or Madness", "text": " &lt;a href=\"Ego%20Draconis%20quests\"&gt;side quest&lt;/a&gt; is given by &lt;a href=\"Eugene\"&gt;Eugene&lt;/a&gt;, a man who has two people trapped in his body; Jackal and Clyde in \"\". \nDetailed Walkthrough.\nEugene, is a ragged man that keeps swinging his axe. He can be found near a tree that's next to the river adjacent to &lt;a href=\"Noryfundus\"&gt;Noryfundus&lt;/a&gt;' shop and across a road near the &lt;a href=\"Bandit%20camp\"&gt;Bandit camp&lt;/a&gt; entrance. Speak with him and agree to find a doctor. \nGo back to the &lt;a href=\"Broken%20Valley%20Village\"&gt;Broken Valley Village&lt;/a&gt; by using the &lt;a href=\"Quarry%20Shrine\"&gt;Quarry Shrine&lt;/a&gt;. Once in the village go to the &lt;a href=\"Black%20Boar\"&gt;Black Boar&lt;/a&gt; Inn, head to the first floor and in the first room speak with &lt;a href=\"Doctor%20Needleman\"&gt;Doctor Needleman&lt;/a&gt;.\nDoctor Needleman will provide a cure that will kill the other personality. This decision will have an effect on which item is received as a reward. After you making a decision by obtaining &lt;a href=\"Potion%20to%20Kill%20Clyde\"&gt;Potion to Kill Clyde&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"Potion%20to%20Kill%20Jackal\"&gt;Potion to Kill Jackal&lt;/a&gt;, return to Eugene. Give him the potion and either Clyde or Jackal will be left in the body."}
{"id": "4617", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=4617", "title": "Michael's Raft", "text": " is a raft wrecked upon temple ruins south of the &lt;a href=\"Battle%20Tower\"&gt;Battle Tower&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nLayout.\nYou can meet Michael on the Sentinel Island but he will just let you know that he is building a raft. Later in the game, you have to go back to the island in your dragon form to search for his raft and land on it as a human. To find it, look on the top right side of the map and fly to the south. It is actually off the map, where there is no poison cloud anymore. Once you locate the raft and land on it, pick up Michael's diary and the achievement unlocks."}
