{"id": "19665", "revid": "27868532", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=19665", "title": "Naberius Storage", "text": " is a &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Knight%20Saga%20Locations\"&gt;dungeon&lt;/a&gt; in northern &lt;a href=\"Broken%20Valley\"&gt;Broken Valley&lt;/a&gt;. It is accessible via the teleporter outside of &lt;a href=\"Old%20Cave\"&gt;old cave&lt;/a&gt; and by &lt;a href=\"Mindread\"&gt;Mindread&lt;/a&gt;ing &lt;a href=\"Naberius\"&gt;Naberius&lt;/a&gt; to get the password to the door. The teleporter also requires a password, found by completing the unmarked quest involving &lt;a href=\"Parchment%20%28Ego%20Draconis%29\"&gt;parchments&lt;/a&gt;.\nBackground.\n&lt;a href=\"Naberius\"&gt;Naberius&lt;/a&gt; uses this dungeon as storage for his necromancy practice.\nLayout.\nThe inside is a narrow straight line of cave that ends up at a storage room containing multiple chests with loot. There are undead enemies on the way, as well as &lt;a href=\"Droxlerite\"&gt;Droxlerite&lt;/a&gt; veins to mine."}
