{"id": "20236", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=20236", "title": "Nemesis Expansion (DOS Boardgame)", "text": "Nemesis Expansion is an expansion released for \"\" by &lt;a href=\"Larian%20Studios\"&gt;Larian Studios&lt;/a&gt;. \nDescription.\nNemesis Expansion is the second official expansion for the \"Divinity Original Sin: The Board Game\" alongside &lt;a href=\"Haunted%20Keep%20Expansion%20%28DOS%20Boardgame%29\"&gt;Haunted Keep&lt;/a&gt; expansion. This expansion is focused on &lt;a href=\"Nemesis\"&gt;Nemesis&lt;/a&gt; a world outside of &lt;a href=\"Rivellon\"&gt;Rivellon&lt;/a&gt;, which used to be populated by the race of &lt;a href=\"Raanaar\"&gt;Raanaar&lt;/a&gt; before they were wiped out by &lt;a href=\"Demons\"&gt;demons&lt;/a&gt; who breached the Raanaars defenses thanks to &lt;a href=\"Damian\"&gt;Damian&lt;/a&gt;s actions. \nNemesis and Haunted Keep expansions were first showcased as part of reaching the final stretchgoal for \"Divinity Original Sin: The Board Game\" where they showed an early preview of the expansions. This expansions narrative and combat design was created by \"Brian Neff\" and \"Noah Conen\". \nThe expansion follows the &lt;a href=\"Godwoken\"&gt;Godwoken&lt;/a&gt; who made a demonic pact with dangerous &lt;a href=\"Demons\"&gt;archdemon&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Adramahlihk\"&gt;Adramahlihk&lt;/a&gt; in exchange for arcane powers. The Godwoken may find themselves in dangerous volcanic world of Nemesis where they will face cursed surfaces and use their newfound power to fight against the treacherous demon. \nThe expansion can be played alongside the Haunted Keep expansion as it is an end-game expansion and occurs after Act 3 of the game. \nContent.\nThis expansion introduces the following:"}
