{"id": "12317", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=12317", "title": "Oily Carapace", "text": "Oily Carapace is a &lt;a href=\"Geomancer%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;Geomancer&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Warfare%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;Warfare&lt;/a&gt; skill in \"\".\nDescription.\nSkill.\n is a supportive mixed skill that allows caster to absorb any ice surface in 2 meter radius from themselves and convert it into Physical Armour. The amount of gained Physical Armour relies on how much oil surface the caster absorbs. \nNote that the Physical Armour gained through this skill will not exceed the maximum amount of Physical Armour of the caster. If the oil surface covers the whole 2 meter radius of the caster it will grant 100 % of the indicated Physical Armour. If the oil surface covers roughly 1 meter radius the skill will restore roughly 30 % of the indicated Physical Armour.\nAlongside restoring Physical Amour this skill will also remove &lt;a href=\"Slowed%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Slowed&lt;/a&gt; status effect.\nSince relies on &lt;a href=\"Geomancy\"&gt;Geomancy&lt;/a&gt; magic it cannot be cast if character is affected by &lt;a href=\"Silenced%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Silenced&lt;/a&gt; status effect.\nScroll and Skillbook.\n skillbook is a magical item that allows its reader to learn skill, if they have at least 1 point into both &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Geomancer\"&gt;Geomancer&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Warfare%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;Warfare&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Attributes%20and%20Abilities%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;abilities&lt;/a&gt;, and use it indefinitely. In order to be able to cast the skill, character needs 1 free memory slot. Note that the book will disappear once read. The book weights 0.5 and its base value is 190 gold. A skillbook can be crafted if a any non-source &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Geomancer\"&gt;Geomancer&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Warfare\"&gt;Warfare&lt;/a&gt; skillbooks are combined. Since is a mixed skill, traders do not have the skillbook for sale.\n is one of the few magic-based skills in the game that does not have a scroll.\nSkill Modifiers.\n is a supportive skill whose effects depend on the following characteristics of the caster:\nOutside of the Level of the caster only their &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Geomancer\"&gt;Geomancer&lt;/a&gt; ability can influence the amount of Physical Armour gained by . \n properties can be affected by talents and other skills only. \nLocations.\nTraders.\nThis skill cannot be bought or stolen from NPCs in the game."}
