{"id": "14372", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=14372", "title": "Ygerna's memory", "text": "Ygerna's Memory is a location in \"\" and in \"&lt;a href=\"Child%20of%20the%20Chaos\"&gt;Child of Chaos novella&lt;/a&gt;\".\nBackground.\nIn 1233 AD &lt;a href=\"Lucian%20the%20Divine\"&gt;Lucian the Divine&lt;/a&gt; executed &lt;a href=\"Ygerna\"&gt;Ygerna&lt;/a&gt; in this room, known as a paladins court. This event set in motion many other events which would change the history of &lt;a href=\"Rivellon\"&gt;Rivellon&lt;/a&gt;. \nWalkthrough.\nThe room is very small and full of enemies. The moment the battle starts the player should jump away from the entrance. After that the player should use his creature or other summoning spells to draw away the attention of\u00a0enemies and focus on bosses.\u00a0"}
