{"id": "15335", "revid": "53418829", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=15335", "title": "A Murderer in Verdistis", "text": " is a &lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity%20quests\"&gt;side quest&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity\"&gt;Divine Divinity&lt;/a&gt;\".\nWalkthrough.\n&lt;a href=\"Kratus\"&gt;Kratus&lt;/a&gt; is having trouble with a murder spree in &lt;a href=\"Verdistis\"&gt;Verdistis&lt;/a&gt;, initially suspecting the &lt;a href=\"Assassins%20Guild\"&gt;Assassins Guild&lt;/a&gt;. The corpses were found sucked dry of blood, which doesn't fit the modus operandi of an assassination. Kratus has a second suspect: &lt;a href=\"Pierce\"&gt;Pierce&lt;/a&gt;, since a witness saw an individual leaving his shop.\nHead east to &lt;a href=\"Pierce%27s%20Wine%20Barrel\"&gt;Pierce's Wine Barrel&lt;/a&gt; and speak to Pierce who claims to have been asleep the nights of the murders; to help clear his name he grants &lt;a href=\"Lucian\"&gt;Lucian&lt;/a&gt; permission to search his shop. Head south then west to the cellar entrance, into the cellar proper. Against the northern wall are several stacked boxes; move these away to discover a coffin with the &lt;a href=\"vampire\"&gt;vampire&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Tutamun\"&gt;Tutamun&lt;/a&gt; sleeping inside.\nSpeaking with Tutamun confirms Pierce's innocence: the vampire had used hypnosis to hide his presence from the shop owner. If he was encountered in &lt;a href=\"Aleroth\"&gt;Aleroth&lt;/a&gt;, he will also confirm to have been speaking to George (and to killing him if &lt;a href=\"George%20Murdered%21\"&gt;George's body&lt;/a&gt; was found after his murder). Deeming Lucian to be a threat, he will turn hostile and must be killed. \nOnce Tutamun is dead, return to Kratus to inform him of the true culprit and his death. This will improve Lucian's &lt;a href=\"reputation\"&gt;reputation&lt;/a&gt; with Kratus by 5."}
