{"id": "2154", "revid": "27868532", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=2154", "title": "A Private Delivery", "text": "A Private Delivery is a &lt;a href=\"Ego%20Draconis%20quests\"&gt;side quest&lt;/a&gt; given by &lt;a href=\"Dana\"&gt;Dana&lt;/a&gt; at &lt;a href=\"Jackson%27s%20farm\"&gt;Jackson's farm&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nDetailed Walkthrough.\nDana will ask the &lt;a href=\"The%20Dragon%20Knight\"&gt;Dragon Slayer&lt;/a&gt; to deliver a letter to Derk, the blacksmith in &lt;a href=\"Broken%20Valley%20Village\"&gt;Broken Valley Village&lt;/a&gt; and requests that the letter reaches him sealed. At this stage, the seal can be broken and the letter read, revealing that Derk and Dana are having an affair. Taking the letter to Carl at this stage and making him aware of the affair will result in the quest failing and Dana being expelled from the farm by Carl.\nTaking the letter to Derk will result in quest completion; however, if the seal is broken, Derk will confront the Slayer about reading the letter, yet takes it no further due to the good news and raises his prices. If the letter was unread he will lower his prices and temporarily leave his smithy to meet Dana."}
