{"id": "15273", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=15273", "title": "Antx", "text": " is the &lt;a href=\"imp\"&gt;imp&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity%20characters\"&gt;member&lt;/a&gt; of the &lt;a href=\"Council%20of%20Seven\"&gt;Council of Seven&lt;/a&gt; and former &lt;a href=\"Black%20Ring\"&gt;Black Ring&lt;/a&gt; agent in 1218 AD.\nBackground.\nA former member of the &lt;a href=\"Black%20Ring\"&gt;Black Ring&lt;/a&gt;, Antx sought safety in a realm contained in a crystal ball. Hiding in the building to the north of the realm, with the key in the possession of &lt;a href=\"Leeandra\"&gt;Leeandra&lt;/a&gt;, queen of the bees, he remained in hiding until the arrival of &lt;a href=\"Lucian\"&gt;Lucian&lt;/a&gt; to convince him to join the &lt;a href=\"Council%20of%20Seven\"&gt;Council of Seven&lt;/a&gt;.\nJoining the council, Antx takes part in the ritual to ascend Lucian to divinity. During the ritual, &lt;a href=\"Janus%20Ferol\"&gt;Janus Ferol&lt;/a&gt; and a troop of &lt;a href=\"orc\"&gt;orc&lt;/a&gt;s invade the chambers, killing Antx in the battle that ensued."}
